        <p>
            Bossbots are one of the four tiers of cogs found in Toontown. This group represents 
            the management of the cogs, being the top of the coprorate ladder. They are the top ranked cogs. 
            The Bossbot Headquarters is the home of the Bossbots. The boss of all Bossbots is the Chief Executive Officer,
            which toons can battle in Bossbot HQ.
        </p>
