        <h2 id="hq">Bossbot HQ</h2>
        <p>
            Bossbot Headquarters, or often referred to as Bossbot HQ, is the base of all Bossbot operations.
            The entrace is located in <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Golfing">Chip N' Dales MiniGolf Playground</a>. 
            You surely cannot miss the dark and gloomy tunnel in the minigolf playground! When visiting this headquarters, 
            toons can access the Clubhouse and Cog Golf Courses. There is the Executive Office Tower, 
            however, this is not accessible yet!
        </p>
